Origin

Kyra Hanson was a vampire who doesn't believe in any kind of violence. She ran the Red House, a place where vampires in crisis can take shelter. She guided journalist Yuki Nitobe through the vampire community. She was trusted by many vampires. However, the Red House was bombed and the explosion killed Kyra.
